# pouring spheres into box made of triangles

units		    lj
atom_style	    sphere
boundary        f f f
dimension	    3
comm_modify     vel yes

region          box block -10 10 -10 10 -10 10 units box
create_box	    2 box   # simply for dump_modify to color lines = green
Created orthogonal box = (-10 -10 -10) to (10 10 10)
  1 by 1 by 1 MPI processor grid

pair_style	    granular
pair_coeff	    * * hooke 4000.0 100.0                     tangential linear_history 1000.0 1.0 0.5 				    damping mass_velocity

neighbor	    0.3 bin
neigh_modify	delay 0 every 1 check yes

fix             20 all surface/global input stl 2 surf.tri.stl                 model * * granular hooke 4000.0 100.0                     tangential linear_history 1000.0 1.0 0.5                     damping mass_velocity
